Oct 2023 • Couples
Great biking tour, with our amazing tour guide Vu! The tour was a nice combination of everything: sightseeing in Hoi An, learning about local life, history, culture & nature, and a boat trip. Especially the food garden was very informative. Vu provided a lot of information and was able to answer all of our questions.
