Regina d
1 contribution
Wonderful way to see Hoi An's countryside
The activity packed cycling tour was such a great way to see Hoi An's countryside. Our guide Vu took us on a fun and interesting route, stopping off at an organic vegetable farm, rice fields complete with a buffalo ride, and the traditional round fishing boat ride. It was such a lovely day being outdoors and getting to know a bit of Hoi An's traditional way of life. Vu was very knowledgeable about the area and expertly navigated us through our biking route. Highly recommend!
Written September 18, 2023
